* Revert "Ignore unexported glyphs"
* Ignore missing date
* Ignore unexported glyphs
* Fix VFJ test

2.0.0 (2020-01-25)
------------------

* Rewrite to load in font data directly instead of proxying. New interface.
* Fix anchors, color loading
* Add variable font abstraction layer



